OOC: Last I checked, these two were out looking for the remains of 
the Clan ship - that puts them in good position, I think.

Wheeljack-X::

Jackie pulls up short and transforms to robot mode as he sees the 
ship impact some distance away.  "Did you see that?" he asks Ragnar.

--- In nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com, EmprzAnastazia@a... wrote:
> Ahhh. ok.. I figured that. Just wanted to verify.
> 
> IC: 
> 
> Placed the shuttle upon Automatic for a moment as she went over to 
another 
> computer to analyze the data she gain after making a brief hack 
into the 
> memory core. Plus her little run in with Alpha Trion & Vector Sigma 
gave her 
> a little insight. But .. not much. 
> 
> She gazed at the screen after entering the information. According 
to records, 
> several were run off of Cybertron & to... 
> 
> "Earth," she was stunned to see the information. 
> 
> Moving back over to the controls, she punched in the coordinate for 
Earth. 
> 
> **************************
> After some time of space flight, the shuttle neared Earth. Maxima 
walked 
> towards the controls-
> 
> SKKREEE!! SSKKREEEEEEE!!!SSKKREEEE!!!
> 
> The ship shuddered as the alarms sounded. She stumbled as she made 
her way to 
> the controls quickly. Feverishly moving over the controls to regain 
the ship, 
> she noticed that an energy reading ahead of her was off the charts. 
> 
> "What the-"
> 
> A bright flash of light... energy coursed through the ship as it 
shocked her. 
> 
> 
> "Ahhhh!" the blue bolts stunned her, knocking her from the seat 
next to the 
> controls to the floor.. she fell inconscious/offline soon there 
after. 
> 
> ****************************
> 
> The Cybertronian shuttle appeared in Prehistoric Earth's orbit. It 
tumbled 
> for a while, then it streaked towards Earth as it was pulled by the 
gravity 
> of the planet. 
> 
> Over the skies, a fireball was seen as the shuttle was burning up 
upon entry, 
> eventually crashing into the body of land that would become the 
North 
> America. 
> 
> The ship smoked, the only passenger inside was offiline & 
unconscious. 
> 
> 
> OOC: I leave it up to who ever wishes to discover her first.
